================ Construction ================
Tested with phpnuke version  : 5.0.1
                               Netscape Navigator 4.77 (Linux)
			       Internet Explorer 5.5
			       Mozilla 0.8
Base                         : ExtraLite (New Version for 5.0 Beta 3)
Editor(s) and Utilities used : Internal File Editor Midnight Commander
Known Bugs                   : None
Build Time                   : 2 Hours


================ Installation ================
Place the file in the theme directory of phpnuke and
run 'tar zxvf filename.tar.gz'
Do not change the directory name without changing the paths
to the images that comes with this package.


